review: Dr. Khushboo is a wonderful dentist. I am not very fond of going to dentists, but when I visited Dr Khushboo, it was not so scary. She really made me feel comfortable and my Root canal procedure went without any hiccups whatsoever. I would definitely recommend someone who is scared of dentists to go to her clinic.

review: Dent-o-care dental clinic was bright n pleasing. I had my front teeth crooked so i went there. All the treatment  procedure  was explained  properly n doctor did my filling so nicely dat it looks natural.. No 1can make out..my smile is improved a lot. Thanks to the doctor for doing wonderful work.
